comments: Curry (PHI) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Wilson (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Embiid (PHI) in the post.
Trent Jr. (TOR) reaches in and makes contact to Curry's (PHI) right arm, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Boucher (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Replay review of the foul on Boucher (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Boucher's arm is not in a vertical position when he makes contact to Harris's (PHI) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) places a hand on Siakam's (TOR) waist during his shooting motion but the contact is marginal.
Boucher (TOR) makes incidental contact with Harris's (PHI) hand that is considered part of the ball during his shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) jumps forward and makes marginal contact with Embiid (PHI) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) places his left arm against Boucher's (TOR) upper body as the two players go for the rebound.  The contact is marginal.
Niang (PHI) is out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Embiid (PHI) moves alongside of Trent Jr. (TOR) on his path to the basket without initiating contact and he legally contests his shot attempt.
Wilson (TOR) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Replay review of the out-of-bounds call on the 76ers pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed successful.  The ball goes off of Siakam's (TOR) foot and he is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Trent Jr. (TOR) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
